   &UR; Engine: &QL; 
5.0-liter V-8, 315 horsepower at 5,600 rpm, 345 pounds-feet of
torque at 3,900 rpm. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Transmission: &QL; 
Five-speed automatic. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Curb weight: &QL; 
4,165 pounds. &QL;
</P>
