<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-27 16:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0136 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SOC-VECSEY-COLUMN-NYT     06-27 0859
