   A CHURCH FINDS A HOME AMID A CITY'S HOMELESS
</P>
<P>
   A0104 BC-EXP-PRESIDENTIAL-POWER-REVIEW-NYT 416 15:52 U A
</P>
<P>
   UNDER CLINTON, THE PRESIDENTIAL PEN IS MIGHTIER THAN EVER
</P>
<P>
   A0102 BC-EXP-NYC-BED&AMP;BREAKFAST-NYT 465 15:50 U A
</P>
<P>
   IT'S TENANTS VS. TOURISTS AT NEW YORK'S ILLEGAL B&AMP;BS
</P>
<P>
   A0100 BC-PRESIDENTIAL-POWER-REVIEW-NYT 1166 15:48 U A
